gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 145, Raptors 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Raptors, 145-113. Lauri Markkanen led the Jazz with 22 points (4-6 3PM) and nine rebounds, while Jordan Clarkson added 21 points and five assists in the victory. Pascal Siakam tallied 27 points, four rebounds, and two assists for the Raptors in the loss. The Jazz improve to 20-20 in the regular season, while the Raptors fall to 15-24.
